cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.IR. 

The paper deals with recognizing human attributes and actions in still images, which is a problem in computer vision. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes an algorithm for learning discriminative templates, which involves machine learning techniques, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. Additionally, the paper involves the use of algorithms to mine parts and learn templates, which falls under the category of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also deals with semantic description of humans, which is related to multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR).
